---
title: Indonesian Style Baby Corn Curry with rice and crunchy peanuts
description: With scallion, lime, ginger and lemongrass all present in this recipe, it's a dish that can definitely be described as fragrant. Delicious is another way to talk about the tender baby corn and carrot that are coated with a spicy and slightly sweet sauce and piled atop a heaping helping of beautiful jasmine rice.
